Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:43.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.90,0:00:50.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.39,0:00:52.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you're headed to Mistral?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.73,0:00:54.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.04,0:00:58.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I heard that they have great food and lots of women...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.42,0:01:01.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's been a few years since the war ended.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:04.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a good thing that we're still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.07,0:01:04.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:07.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Glenb!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.84,0:01:10.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How can you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.76,0:01:15.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seems like you're awake, little missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:18.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Here's some of our war bounty...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.85,0:01:22.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah, it's caramel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:27.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}T-Thank you for giving me something so expensive!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:29.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Erm... Sergeant!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.98,0:01:31.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.07,0:01:36.15,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If we treat the trumpeter well, we'll be able to hear the retreat calls better...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.15,0:01:40.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We don't really get a lot of new recruits due to the recall of the draft.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:41.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Did you volunteer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.72,0:01:44.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes! So I could learn how to play instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:45.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.29,0:01:47.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Uhh... I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.01,0:01:50.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's fine to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.59,0:01:52.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do your best, little missy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.50,0:01:54.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Private 2nd class, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:55.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:58.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}My name is Sorami Kananta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:11.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}There's a festival today at Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:12.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:14.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why we've stopped here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:22.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:26.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the position you've been assigned, the Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:28.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Head in that direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.22,0:04:29.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:40.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Order: "Private 2nd class, Sorami Kanata, will be assigned to the 1121 Platoon of Trois State, Seize."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:44.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}"Helvetia Republic Army Headquarters."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:04:57.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Objective completed at 1320 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.64,0:04:59.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:14.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The city of water and glass, Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.07,0:05:18.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:21.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm expected to report at 1500 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:25.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can finally let you sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:30.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Direction check...{\alpha&HFF&} Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Direction check... Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:32.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Time check...{\alpha&HFF&} Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.58,0:05:33.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Time check... Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:35.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gear check... {\alpha&HFF&}Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:36.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Gear check... Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:37.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Advance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:38.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.79,0:06:19.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}D-flat, what a beautiful sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:23.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's a fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:26.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}10.25 yen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What a beautiful doll...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.43,0:06:41.97,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What's wrong, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.97,0:06:44.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A kitten that got too excited from the festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.76,0:06:47.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}... It ran at full speed towards tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:49.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.83,0:06:52.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Little kittens are supposed to wander...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:55.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why they're cute, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.63,0:07:00.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It would have been fine, if it were a stray...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:00.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:04.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}However, this one has an owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That startled me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But once again, I'm able to find another beautiful place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:40.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.14,0:07:40.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:52.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh? A soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.15,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A girl from the fortress?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:55.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This one looks cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:58.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thanks for the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.73,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Now you've done it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:25.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Aim and... Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:27.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.97,0:08:29.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.99,0:08:52.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:55.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:57.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Getting involved with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:59.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What are you planning to do with your uniform looking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:08.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Bless you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.72,0:09:09.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:17.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:31.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How's the bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:33.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:35.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.81,0:09:39.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seems like you were an easy target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.24,0:09:41.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You weren't able to dodge it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.74,0:09:47.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The dye will come off once it dries...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No need to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.24,0:09:52.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Um... That was a festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:54.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It is a day of legend in Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.81,0:09:56.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A legend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.45,0:09:57.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What kind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:03.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The Fire Maidens who guard the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:16.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:19.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The repairs for that are completed as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.80,0:10:24.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Also... This.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:29.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Felicia, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.54,0:10:33.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That nuisance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.58,0:10:35.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Late...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:36.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Late! Late!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:38.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Lateeeeee!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:41.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And we came all the way here just to pick her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:41.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.46,0:10:44.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's just wait here patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.42,0:10:48.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was a present from your father right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:50.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.61,0:10:58.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you for the wonderful bath!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:02.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't know why, but I always get lost easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.63,0:11:05.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But because of that, I had such a wonderful meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:07.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:10.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But try not to get lost around here, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.34,0:11:11.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:14.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.53,0:11:25.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You can distinguish the notes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:37.26,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It has a very clear sound, and seems to bring back memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's not what I meant-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:41.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:42.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:52.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:55.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Were you going to give up your life for something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:57.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But that bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.67,0:12:01.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.47,0:12:05.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was meant to be like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:12.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.57,0:12:17.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.84,0:12:29.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.83,0:12:32.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have something to attend to, so I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:33.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't get lost again, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.58,0:12:37.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:39.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It must have been a very important item...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.25,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}From there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.79,0:13:06.26,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Advance forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}The Fire Maidens?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:05.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}Long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.95,0:14:10.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}Long before the world became the way it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.07,0:14:17.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}Under the valley of this city, there lived a winged demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:30.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}The demon spread fire and shook the ground, causing everyone to suffer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:37.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}Eventually, it took away all the maidens living in the fortress
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:41.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}and trapped them inside an underground maze...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:50.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}However, the maidens did not give in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:56.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}They summoned each\N> other, using the golden horns given by God and escaped the maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:15:06.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}With the support\N> of a giant spider, they defeated the demon and beheaded it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:11.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}After they beheaded the demon, violent flames erupted forth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.83,0:15:16.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}At the rate the fire was spreading, the town would have burned down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.48,0:15:20.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}In order to stop the fire, the maidens embraced the demon's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.56,0:15:31.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}From then on, the villagers continued pouring water on the maidens and the demon's head every day...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:35.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}After a year, the fire was finally put out...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.97,0:15:40.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}And so, to comfort the spirits of the maidens who have sacrificed to save the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.61,0:15:43.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}the water spraying festival was created.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:41.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The new girl... didn't come after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That doesn't matter anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.66,0:16:46.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Take a look Captain, it's Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:49.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seems like she fits the role perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:52.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess I was correct in entrusting her with this task.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:55.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh? But didn't we draw lots...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:04.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seems like I got lost again...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.61,0:17:09.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm... so worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.57,0:17:21.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sometimes, being lost may be fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:27.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...because you get to meet people who you haven't met before...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:34.15,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want... to be alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.83,0:17:36.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}Are you lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:39.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}Yes, I want to see my mommy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.46,0:17:40.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}It will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.95,0:17:44.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}If you wish for it hard enough,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:47.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}that feeling of wanting to see her will reach her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:48.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.42,0:17:51.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}The sound will always resonate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:54.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Always resonate...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:57.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}Always resonate, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:01.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}And so it will be heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.80,0:18:06.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the resting place of the Fire Maidens.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.69,0:18:10.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Embracing the demon, and relieving the curse...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.53,0:18:14.15,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In order to not let it awaken once more...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:15.74,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.44,0:18:17.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The sound of the golden horn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:19.45,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Could it be that the demon has...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:20.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Awakened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.52,0:18:22.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kureha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.10,0:18:34.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}Hear it... someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:37.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\i1}My sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.40,0:18:50.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.16,0:18:58.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The sound resonated, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.24,0:19:03.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Wake up already...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.56,0:19:05.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Private, second class Sorami Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:10.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.17,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This place is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.17,0:19:15.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just how long were you intending to sleep in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the Time-Telling Fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:20.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The station of the 1121 platoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}About yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:41.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I-I am very sorry to have troubled you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:45.12,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.29,0:19:47.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.42,0:19:51.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But don't do something so reckless again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.62,0:19:54.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Just for a bell like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:17.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.58,0:20:19.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A trumpet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:23.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...why this fortress is called the Time-Telling Fortress.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:01.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The sounds of the skies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:38.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Kazumiya Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:41.18,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:44.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will train you to become a trumpeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.75,0:21:50.16,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nice to meet you Major Sergeant Rio!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.16,0:21:51.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rio is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:52.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's Felicia's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.96,0:21:56.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Our Captain's policy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We do not talk about ranks here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:21:59.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:01.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.98,0:22:02.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Rio-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.68,0:22:05.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All right then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.42,0:22:08.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:09.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Blow the morning call!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:29.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The trumpet girl is bad this time.
